title: Fushigi no Umi no Nadia Omake Gekijou
synopsis: While Nadia has been licensed by ADV, the Omake "extra" episodes were not. These short Omake "extra" episodes were included as a bonus on the Japanese LD set. They were never released on any other format.
characters: ['la Arwall, Nadia', 'Roque Lartigue, Jean', 'King', 'Carlsberg, Marie en', 'Nemo', 'Gargoyle', 'Electra, Medina La Lugensius', 'Narrator']
